<!--
  This file documents the routing structure for versioned/i18n documentation.
  
  In production, this would be implemented as a catch-all route that:
  1. Parses the URL to extract version, language, section, and slug
  2. Resolves the content using resolveDoc()
  3. Handles fallbacks for missing translations
  4. Renders the page with appropriate SEO metadata
  
  For now, the existing routes in /pages/components/, /pages/foundations/, etc.
  continue to work and will be gradually migrated to this unified structure.
